My PM Routine 💕
⁃  Pink Cloud Cleanser: a super gentle cleanser that takes off all my makeup while leaving my skin feeling clean and hydrated. I love to steam after cleansing to help open up my pores
⁃  Bakuchiol Serum: targets signs of fine lines, helps with texture and any sort of dullness to help maintain my youthful glow
⁃  Lapis Face Oil: This is amazing for acne-prone skin! I like to incorporate this around ‘that time of the month’ to prevent any crazy bumps from popping up.
⁃  Jade Roller: Helps to reduce puffiness *tip* I store this in my fridge for a cooling effect that helps de-puff my skin.
⁃  Rose Hibiscus Hydrating Facial Mist: I live for drenching my face in this amazing mist. It has amazing ingredients like Rose, Aloe, + Coconut water to hydrate and soothe my skin.
